Dominique Zardi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dominique_Zardi 0 Dominique Zardi (born Emile Jean Cohen-Zardi) (2 March 1930, Paris – 13 December 2009) was a French actor. He acted in more than 600 films, including Fantômas with Louis De Funès and Jean Marais. He died of cancer at the age of 79.
